caption.body: Our photography exhibition, "United States Coast Guard Air Station San Francisco: Honoring the Guardians of the Golden Gate 75th" has been extended until the end of next month!  See this exhibition, pre-security, in the Aviation Museum and Library. The Aviation Museum is open daily, from 10am to 4:30pm, except holidays. http://bit.ly/1XRNG3e
